main event: Observation of two contrails reported over Pepperrell AFB on 20 February 1964.
interesting points: The sighting was made using ground radar,The contrails were of unknown nationality,The length of observation was noted as 1 1 1 S, The report concluded the sighting was likely a balloon, The report includes communication to various military authorities.
location: Pepperrell AFB, Newfoundland and Labrador, Canada
